  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "description",
      "abstract": "Establishes a Regular Session Review Working Group to determine the essential timing and effective framework for a lengthened legislative session calendar for election and non-election years.  Requires the Working Group to submit a report of its findings and recommendations, including any proposed legislation, to the Legislature before the convening of the Regular Session of 2028.  Requires the Legislative Reference Bureau to assist the Working Group in finalizing its report and drafting any proposed legislation.  Appropriates fund.  Effective 7/1/2525.  (SD1)"
    }
  ],
